description: [``botocore``] boto3 no longer overwrites user supplied `Content-Encoding` with `aws-chunked` when user also supplies `ChecksumAlgorithm`.
[``botocore``] This release adds filter support ListAnomalyForInsight API.

[``botocore``] This release will enable customer select INCREMENTAL as ImportModel in Forecast's CreateDatasetImportJob API. Verified latest SDK containing required attribute, following https://w.amazon.com/bin/view/AWS-Seer/Launch/Trebuchet/
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM).
[``botocore``] The AWS Elemental MediaTailor SDK for Channel Assembly has added support for program updates, and the ability to clip the end of VOD sources in programs.
